title: 求助 安装林业mod NEI查看合成表 会退出
author: 赵大官人
txt_content:
States: 'U' = Unloaded 'L' = Loaded 'C' = Constructed 'H' = Pre-initialized 'I' = Initialized 'J' = Post-initialized 'A' = Available 'D' = Disabled 'E' = Errored

显示这个错误 怎么破  求大神指点!!

replies.author: wangkang48
replies.txt_content: 跟某个NEI的扩展冲突，把那个扩展升到最新版可以解决

replies.author: 赵大官人
